title: [GAMEPLAY] Alistar W on Morgana
body:
Abilities didn't work on Morgana. W for sure, possibly Q.  Headbutt went right by Morgana.  Multiple times so I was reproducible in game.

Nov.28 around 1:30 EST

replies.body:
Was Morgana spell-shielding during your headbutt? If so, she would have negated any headbutt effects. If she wasn't spell-shielding, I'd like you to record some gameplay and send me a snippet so I can see the issue reproduced.

Let me know if you have any questions.
